00:12:50.000 --> 00:12:52.000
Great. Nice work, Morty.

249
00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:57.000
Ugh.

250
00:13:04.000 --> 00:13:08.000
Ooh, look at you, C-137. You're, aren't you a tough customer?

251
00:13:08.000 --> 00:13:10.000
The slow clap? Really?

252
00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:17.000
Kinda played out, dude. Not in this dimension it isn't. In fact, I invented it. Nobody else has ever even done it here before.

253
00:13:17.000 --> 00:13:18.000
Well, la di da.

254
00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:20.000
Hey, that's mine!

255
00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:26.000
